{"id":279382,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-快讯：在广州街头举牌抗议朝鲜核爆的维/","date":"2013-02-16T08:31:03Z","modified":"2013-02-16T08:31:03Z","title":"维权网 | 快讯：在广州街头举牌抗议朝鲜核爆的维权人士被警察带走（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3></h3>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span></span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span>，参与广州举牌抗议朝鲜核爆的维权人士，在行至广州天河城时与警察发生冲突，徐琳、张圣雨、孙德胜、张茂中等人被警察带走。参与上午举牌的湖南籍网友成秋波对外打出电话（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18874211488</span><span>）称：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>徐琳被抓</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>，话还没有说完，就挂断电话，随即，他的电话也无人接听。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>）上午，维权人士秀才江湖（吴斌）、张圣雨、张茂中、徐琳、成秋波等人在广州街头举牌，表达立场，抗议朝鲜在靠近中国东北边境地区进行核爆试验，他们打算下午继续举牌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>近日以来，中国公民在街头对朝鲜核爆表示抗议的活动经常遭中国警方干扰，例如，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，安徽省合肥市庐阳区逍遥津公园门口，网友柴宝文（新浪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ID:@</span><span>我们不是下等人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>合肥</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span>举牌抗议朝鲜核试爆，随后被当地国保带走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2013/02/blog-post_9080.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2013/02/blog-post_9080.html</a></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-iO5VfzJNPls/UR8vSdRO5sI/AAAAAAAAdLo/PvbvNPuiDso/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" h